From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Jul 2026 18:27:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 3/4] feat(investor): build core investor marketplace features
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Public /opportunities browse page — unauthenticated, filterable by
  asset class, location, min investment, investor type; deal cards with
  compliance disclaimer and CTA to register
- Email notifications on introduction decisions (approve, decline,
  request_info, require_nda), program approval, and investor profile
  approval — all wrapped in try/catch so email failures never block API
- GET /investor/introductions backend route revealing developer contact
  info only when status is approved or intro_made
- MyIntroductions.tsx page with contact reveal section, status messaging
  per state, financials, and empty-state CTA
- App.tsx + Shell.tsx wired for /opportunities (public) and
  /my-introductions (authenticated)
- Landing.tsx Browse Deals nav link

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_015P4doGB5hmHfHAYu31btqA
